					 In this article 
						 THIS TOPIC APPLIES TO:   SQL Server (starting with 2017) Azure SQL Database Azure SQL Data Warehouse  Parallel Data Warehouse    Automatic tuning is a database feature that provides insight into potential query performance problems, recommend solutions, and automatically fix identified problems. 
 Automatic tuning in SQL Server 2017 notifies you whenever a potential performance issue is detected, and lets you apply corrective actions,
or lets the  Database Engine automatically fix performance problems.
Automatic tuning in SQL Server 2017 enables you to identify and fix performance issues caused by  SQL plan choice regressions . Automatic tuning in  Azure SQL Database cre